      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is definitely a diamond in the rough, currently in poor condition and needing significant mechanical and cosmetic work to get back to its best. It's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a hobbyist looking for a budget-friendly way to own this model and build it exactly how they want!",
