    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car drives smoothly, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear and tear from regular use. It is a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by a single owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the leather or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having followed a strict maintenance schedule at authorized dealerships. This is a rare find for a collector or a buyer who demands a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its consistent performance and well-preserved mechanical state. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive professional evaluation, ensuring it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal. Offering a sophisticated driving experience and a history of diligent maintenance, this selection represents an optimal balance of longevity and value for the serious investor. We invite you to inspect this exemplary model at your earliest convenience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, running smoothly and ready for many more miles. It\u2019s perfect if you need something reliable that\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of. I'd love for you to come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 29800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam timing. The power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement with plates and a cooling system refresh with a high-flow aluminum radiator. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, benefiting from refreshed control arm bushings and a factory-spec alignment. While the exterior shows minor road-rash and the interior exhibits light bolster wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains a testament to BMW M engineering. This is a high-performance tool optimized for mechanical purity and visceral feedback.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine and clean interior. Reliable daily driver. No major mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of its class, offering a perfect balance of reliability and comfort. The exterior finish remains vibrant and smooth, with only minor surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, you will find a pristine, non-smoker cabin where the premium upholstery shows only light signs of use and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has undergone regular oil changes and safety inspections, with the most recent service completed just last month. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brake system provides firm, responsive stopping power. This car drives straight and quiet, reflecting its history of responsible ownership. It is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. It offers a sophisticated driving experience characterized by dependable performance and a well-preserved interior. This is a premier selection for those seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that bridges the gap between luxury and value. Detailed service records are available upon request for serious inquiries.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
